{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_20051.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"Ayame","narration":"The director died.","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"At first, she said she was just real tired.@She said she was takin' a short break..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","chara":[{"id":800800,"motion":100,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"The Director","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"I'm all right, Ayame. I'll be better before@you know it...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"textCenter":"You see, there are still so many things@I have to do..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narration":"She told me that...","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"But then right after,@she went to Heaven..."},{"narration":"She fell sick and then... @It happened so fast..."},{"narration":"It was too sudden, I didn't @know what was even goin' on..."},{"narration":"I saw Konoha and Hazuki cryin'@and then I started cryin' too..."},{"narration":"All the sad feelings just overtook @me. I couldn't stop cryin'..."},{"narration":"But it wasn't the time for us@to be cryin'..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_20051.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Ayame","narrationEffect":"out","textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Huh?![chara:302801:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock] Th-the Azalea House is gonna get@torn down?!","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story10","textLeft":"Why?! Whyyy?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Hazuki","textRight":"Oh, Ayame..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":300,"soulGem":0}],"textRight":"Um... How should I say this..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Konoha","textRight":"You're usually so good at explaining things.@This isn't like you..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Hazuki","textRight":"Honestly, I'm still struggling to get my own@feelings in order..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Konoha","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302801,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"soulGem":0}],"textLeft":"Wh-what's gonna happen to us if our home@gets destroyed?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":100,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Konoha","textRight":"I don't know..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":200}],"textBg":"shout","textLeft":"I hate this!"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"textRight":"Ayame..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":200,"soulGem":0}],"textLeft":"Nooo! I hate this! I hate it, I hate it!"},{"textLeft":"The director's gone, and soon the Azalea@House will be too!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302801,"tear":1}],"textLeft":"*Whimper* *Sob*@I hate, hate, hate, haaate it...!"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Hazuki","textRight":"I hate it too, Ayame..."},{"textRight":"You understand that, right?"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Konoha","textRight":"Of course we all hate it..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"textRight":"Why... Just why..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"textRight":"We need to figure this out on our own."},{"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narration":"Konoha and Hazuki tried to save the@Azalea House... But nothing worked.","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"But, but! We all tried super hard!@We tried everythin' we could!"},{"narration":"But in the end..."},{"narration":"We couldn't reverse the decision to @shut down the Azalea House..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Ayame","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":0,"soulGem":0}],"textCenter":"But guess what!"},{"bg":"bg_adv_20051.jpg","narration":"Azalea House never got shut down!","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"You wanna know why?!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}